    {
        "content": "<p>What you're describing is not \"congruent argument\", but injectivity</p>",
        "id": 478019683,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1729507330
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And unfortunately, the rewrite you want to do amounts to the statement you were trying to prove in the first place; so I think you need to rethink your proof strategy here!</p>",
